                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d22">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-06-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 9, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received July 3.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 453.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Adverting to my dispatch, No. 446, of the 26th
                    ultimo, I have to report that the House of Deputies, on yesterday, by a vote of
                    93 to 52, refused to present articles of impeachment against Vice-President
                    Peixoto.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">E. H. Conger.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
